line_1: I've done, she mutter'd — I was saying,
line_2: It did not argufy my playing.

line_1: "He's from the land of Walter Scott," they're saying.
line_2: Their rapid lips the whispered words betraying —

line_1: For they come to the Pump, as before I was saying,
line_2: And talk all at once, while the Music is playing:
